        <div>
            <h3>Getting Started With PHP Text Analysis</h3>
            <p>PHP text analysis is already setup on packagist.org so you can easily add text analysis easily to your project. The simplest way to get started is by creating a composer.json file and adding the following text into the json file.</p>
            <code><pre>
{
 "require": {
 "php-text-analysis/php-text-analysis": "1.0.*@dev"
 }
}
                </pre></code>
            
            <p>Now you can install the PHP text analysis by running the following command on your command line</p>
            <code><pre>
                composer.phar install
                </pre></code>
